You cannot have more mana than maximum, so don't waste it.
The dungeon is not actually endless. The Dark Lord awaits.
There is a capital boss every two floors.
Magenta monsters deal 2 damage.
Cyan bosses have two lives.
Black bosses cannot be harmed by bump attacks.
Yellow bosses swap your health and mana scores. Beware!
White bosses drain maximum health!
Blue bosses summon monsters.
Letters with a tittle drain mana.
Vowels can move diagonally.
